actions, the development of language skills and learning strategies, and language learning motivation.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 0aLanguage and languagesxStudy and teaching. 0aSecond language acquisition. 4aAngewandte Linguistik. 4aFremdsprachendidaktik. 4aFremdsprachenerwerb. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh  aLanguage Acquisition, Language Teaching, Language Education, Applied Linguistics.1 aAbe, Yuko, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aChan, Wai Meng, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aChan, Wai Meng, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aChang, Shanmao Frank, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCheng, Hsiao-fang, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aChin, Kwee Nyet, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aChin, Kwee Nyet, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aFinch, Andrew Edward, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHuang, Shenghui Cindy, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aIstanto, Johanna W., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKawaguchi, Yoshikazu, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLaskar, Benjamin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLi, Chen-Ying, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLittlewood, William, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNagami, Masanori, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNagami, Masanori, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aOoi, Ae Kee,